 "Yes, borrowers with multiple properties can potentially establish HELOCs on each, subject to overall debt capacity and qualification:"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "What happens to your HELOC during bankruptcy?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "How does bankruptcy affect HELOC obligations? HELOCs are secured debts treated differently than unsecured obligations:"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Can you convert HELOC balances to fixed-rate loans?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Many lenders offer fixed-rate conversion options providing payment predictability:"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "How do HELOC draws affect your taxes and basis?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Do HELOC draws increase your property's tax basis? Generally no\u2014borrowing against equity doesn't change your cost basis:"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "What credit score impact does opening a HELOC create?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "How does a HELOC affect your credit profile? Opening and managing a HELOC influences multiple credit factors:"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Can you get a HELOC with a reverse mortgage?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Do reverse mortgages and HELOCs work together? Generally no\u2014combining these products faces significant obstacles:"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "How do economic downturns affect HELOC availability?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Can lenders freeze or reduce your HELOC during economic stress? Yes\u2014lenders maintain certain rights to protect against declining property values:"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "What happens to HELOC balances when you pass away?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "How are HELOC debts handled after the borrower's death? HELOCs become part of estate settlement:"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Can you negotiate HELOC terms with lenders?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Are HELOC terms fixed or negotiable? Many aspects of HELOC agreements involve some negotiation potential:"}}]};
